{"tid":603462,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔知你睇唔睇到..唔知你知唔知我講緊你","createTime":"2018-03-23T18:41:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T19:43:48.000Z","uid":146894,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b411435dd09b71c219ad000cefd3e724175aef42","tid":603462,"uid":146894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"一年半嘅感情..<br />\n話長唔長話短唔短<br />\n呢半年幾以黎都好少鬧交 我仲以為可以同你繼續行落去<br />\n點知你突然同我講分手 話拍到攰 冇feel<br />\n又話唔中意我同我屋企人嘅想法同相處方式<br />\n所以唔會有將來所以要分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問你幾時開始冇feel 你話1 2月左右<br />\n問你係咪我做錯啲咩你又話唔係<br />\n我仲求你俾多次機會我再追你一次<br />\n我仲諗埋到時要去邊到 做啲咩 遲啲你生日要點樣點樣<br />\n點知原來你應承我只係為左hea我 唔想我煩住你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n原來你根本就冇諗住真係俾我再追你一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我仲打左一大篇野去同你講冇左我之後你要點點點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n打到我都喊左幾次先打得完篇野<br />\n結果你都係同我講冇可能<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母原來你帽我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔怪得話冇feel就冇feel啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n屌你仲呃我話要減肥唔食夜晚唔同我出街<br />\n原來係要同第二條仔去食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你都算醒目 分左手先po sc <br />\n仲要用返同我當初一模一樣嘅filter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後 如果佢條新仔見到呢個post嘅話 我想同你講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">他朝君體也相同呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同埋你條女隻豬已經俾我食左啦 16歲生日過左兩個月就俾我食左啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲幫你調教好添啦 搵你碌鳩頂住佢個閪就會濕撚曬好想要架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<br />\n[size=6隧道都幫你擴闊埋啦 頭果幾個月屌佢都仲要慢慢入 入完都仲要慢慢郁一陣先可以開波[/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">而加唔洗架啦 前戲都唔洗做直接就可以入曬架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過希望你唔好介意屌空氣啦 除非你有我咁粗咁長可以屌到佢成日叫好粗好入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"1b882954069e793270b89ff29666b0a364ee80ce","tid":603462,"uid":146894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T18:44:30.000Z","msg":"推到上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90111a24907df07c14a097a49c881517cdc38d66","tid":603462,"uid":146894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T18:51:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"259bd88229cf09f3d89dfaf0499fcc47eba43138","tid":603462,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T18:57:03.000Z","msg":"無呀屌"},{"pid":"ecf7556a3c09dcdcd5aeff16ceb8d4cafce6a47f","tid":603462,"uid":146894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"259bd88229cf09f3d89dfaf0499fcc47eba43138","tid":603462,"uid":137997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc